name: Electric Age - Power

quests.name: Solid Infuser
quests.description: Infuse multiple items to get new resources.

quests.name: Assembler
quests.description: Craft an Assembler.

quests.name: Harvesters
quests.description: There are several types of harvesters, like the ore harvester, the loot harvester and much more. You need at least one Space Ripper connected to the Harvester. They consumes a lot of energy.

quests.name: Vacuum Freezer
quests.description: Build a Vacuum Freezer.

quests.name: Replicator
quests.description: The Replicator can use UU-Matter to produce Items. It's one of the most powerful Machines.

quests.name: Cables
quests.description: Energy transportation.

quests.name: Fisher
quests.description: This is a automated fisher.

quests.name: Fusion Power
quests.description: Need more Energy? Try to set up a Fusion Reactor.

quests.name: Nikolite
quests.description: This is the base material for Industrial Revolution. You can find it in rare Spheres in the Starry Sky Dimension.

quests.name: Centrifuge
quests.description: Craft a Centrifuge and provide it with power.

quests.name: Assembling Machine
quests.description: You should immediately use the 2 Advanced Circuits for an Assembling Machine, with which you can then make more of them.

quests.name: Basic Machine Hull
quests.description: The Basic Machine Hull is the core of many LV Machines. Very soon I will be able to build a Turbine to produce Electricity.

quests.name: Tech Reborn
quests.description: Let's start with Tech Reborn. The Standard Machine Casing is needed for several recipes.

quests.name: Extractor
quests.description: Extract rubber from rubber trees.

quests.name: Electrolyzer
quests.description: Build a Electrolyzer.

quests.name: Space Travel Preparations
quests.description: If you want to go into space, you have to prepare. Start by melting some dirt into oxide.

quests.name: Lava Spring
quests.description: This Block can provide you with an infinite Lava Source. But it can also fire Furnacess or brewing stands on its side, but it doesn't work above or below.

quests.name: The End
quests.description:
Search for the end portal by throwing one of these Eye types in the Sky Islands Dimension.
To activate the End Portal you have to collect each of them.
With 4 End Crystals you can summon the Ender Dragon.

quests.name: Quarries
quests.description: The Electric Quarry can process some other Drills to produce some useful resources. The Gold Drill can be used to obtain Netherite.

quests.name: Sky Islands
quests.description: In this Dim you can dicover many Biomes and Strutures. The Portal frame has to be build out of Mossy Glowshroom Caps. The Mossy Glowshroom Sapling can grow on End Moss. To ignite it, right click with the "" Item. It's the Quests reward.

quests.name: Recycler
quests.description: If you have some crap in your storage system, you may whant to recycle it.

quests.name: Generators
quests.description: Extra Generators offers a lot of Generator types.

quests.name: Netherite Funnel
quests.description: Maxing out your free ores production. The Netherite Funnel is the best Funnel you can buld. But it will not provide you with almost ALL ores in the game!

quests.name: Farmer
quests.description: Automate your farms.

quests.name: GraviChestPlate
quests.description: Need a very powerful Chestplate? Try to build the GraviChestplate.

quests.name: Electric Blast Furnace
quests.description: Build a Electric Blast Furnace.

quests.name: Dimensional Applicator
quests.description: This Block can be used to get a permanent effect.

quests.name: Nuclear Energy
quests.description: In Modern Industrialization you can discover much more. Let's try to build the Nuclear Reactor! Details can be found in the Guide Book.

quests.name: Polarizer
quests.description: You can use the Polarizer to make Magnetic Rods much cheaper.

quests.name: Angel Ring
quests.description: This Item can grant you creative Flight.

quests.name: Steam Turbine
quests.description: Craft a Steam Turbine. This block allows you to produce your first Electric Energy.

quests.name: Moon
quests.description: Continue your preparations and follow the directions in the Space Explorer's Guide. Then you should be able to travel to the moon soon. Explore the other celestial bodies as well.

quests.name: Fluid Infuser
quests.description: This machine is able to combine items and fluids.

quests.name: Jetpacks
quests.description: You can fly around with a jetpack. But it needs energy. Lucky for you, there are a ton of different Ones.

quests.name: Compressor
quests.description: Tech Reborn offers various machines that you should already know from Modern Industrialization.

quests.name: Energy Storage
quests.description: This is one option to store energy, but it also allows to charge items.

quests.name: High-Voltage
quests.description: Sure, this chapter didn't take you through all of the machines you might need. The fusion reactor is not easy. Find out for yourself what you need to build it and put it into operation.

description:
Mods like "TechReborn" or "Industrial Revolution" are brought closer to you in this chapter.
You will be shown some important machines here. But slowly you should go your own way
